CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1783521457
OL,3,CBank closure to force 80-mile round
OL,4,Ctrip for customers
OL,6,FSome bank customers in Dumfriesshire
OL,7,Fare set to face journeys of around one
OL,8,Fhour to access their local branch.
OL,10,FThe Bank of Scotland in Dumfries will
OL,11,Fclose for refurbishment in August and
OL,12,FSeptember.
OL,14,FCustomers have been directed to visit
OL,15,Fthe Lloyds Bank in Carlisle during the
OL,16,Fclosure, meaning residents in Moffat
OL,17,Fwill have to make an 80-mile round
OL,18,Ftrip.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1783521457
OL,3,CBank closure to force 80-mile round
OL,4,Ctrip for customers
OL,6,FThe Bank of Scotland shut their branch
OL,7,Fin Moffat in November 2025 citing a
OL,8,Fshift in customers increasingly using
OL,9,Fonline banking.
OL,11,FLocal campaigner Evelyn Atkins said:
OL,12,F"How do they get to Carlisle if they
OL,13,Fdon't have a car?
OL,15,F"66% of our population is over 55 and
OL,16,F24% are over 75, and they're expecting
OL,17,Fpeople in that age group to know how
OL,18,Fto use the internet and to have the
OL,19,Fmoney to keep updating the equipment
OL,20,Fthey need.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1783521457
OL,3,CBank closure to force 80-mile round
OL,4,Ctrip for customers
OL,6,F"They're just not thinking straight at
OL,7,Fall."
OL,9,FEvelyn said visitors are unable to
OL,10,Fwithdraw cash in the town, which is
OL,11,Fbeginning to impact local businesses.
OL,13,FLocal cafe owner Russell Murray has
OL,14,Fstopped banking with the Bank of
OL,15,FScotland after the closure led to
OL,16,Fmonths of making trips to drop off
OL,17,Fcash in Dumfries.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1783521457
OL,3,CBank closure to force 80-mile round
OL,4,Ctrip for customers
OL,6,FHe said: "It's not really viable. It
OL,7,Fcauses the risk of people being aware
OL,8,Fof us taking a lump sum of cash to a
OL,9,Fbranch in Dumfries.
OL,11,F"There's also the cost of fuel to get
OL,12,Fto Dumfries and it's been a nuisance
OL,13,Fto be perfectly honest as well.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1783521457
OL,3,CBank closure to force 80-mile round
OL,4,Ctrip for customers
OL,6,F"For me to take money to Dumfries,
OL,7,Fthat means I have to put extra staff
OL,8,Fon while I'm not here, which again
OL,9,Fcosts the business even more money
OL,10,Fthan it would had I been able to just
OL,11,Fnip 30 seconds down the road to the
OL,12,FMoffat branch, and also have a little
OL,13,Fblether with the staff because it was
OL,14,Fthe social side of things as well.
OL,16,F"It's like you're picking on those
OL,17,Fthat are out in the sticks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1783521457
OL,3,CBank closure to force 80-mile round
OL,4,Ctrip for customers
OL,6,F"We don't all live in cities - think
OL,7,Fof the elders that maybe rely on face-
OL,8,Fto-face service, they've had that
OL,9,Fservice for years and now they're made
OL,10,Fto change. It's a bit unfair I think."
OL,12,FA Bank of Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"We're investing in our Dumfries
OL,14,Fbranch to improve the experience for
OL,15,Four customers, and it will temporarily
OL,16,Fclose while these upgrades are carried
OL,17,Fout.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1783521457
OL,3,CBank closure to force 80-mile round
OL,4,Ctrip for customers
OL,6,F"During this time, customers can
OL,7,Fcontinue their everyday banking at
OL,8,Ftheir nearest Post Office, via our app
OL,9,Fand online, by phone, they can deposit
OL,10,Fcash at a nearby PayPoint location, or
OL,11,Fthey can visit our Community Banker.
OL,13,F"We look forward to welcoming
OL,14,Fcustomers back soon to our improved
OL,15,Fbranch."
OL,26,@wD@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
